					"type": 23,
					"value": "Main dialogue with creepy myconid sovereign. He wants you to kill some duergar that are left from when they attacked these mushroom creatures. Myconids are part of a \"circle\", kind of a hive mind. They speak in visions, with music - all telepathically. This should be otherworldly and slightly disturbing. "
